  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bb2\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A lorry that fell into the Batticaloa Valayiravu river",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "An incident occurred on Friday morning when a heavy lorry veered off the road and fell into the Nether River near Batticaloa Vaunadivu Nether Bridge.",
        "It is understood that the incident took place when two lorries were traveling simultaneously on the said road and one lorry tried to overtake the other.",
        "The driver and conductor of the vehicle escaped unhurt while the vehicle was damaged when it veered off the road and plunged into the river."
      ],
